/F2 11 Tf
12.6499999999999986 TL
0.059 0.09 0.165 rg
44. 490. Td
(What Survives the Scan) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
10.3499999999999996 TL
0.278 0.333 0.412 rg
52. 474. Td
(Trajectory. Response. Functional loss. Trigger logic. Sleep and mood spillover. The details that survive are the ones tied to) Tj
T* (decisions, not the ones written for emotional effect.) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 11 Tf
12.6499999999999986 TL
0.059 0.09 0.165 rg
44. 434. Td
(Where Standardized Measures Fit) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
10.3499999999999996 TL
0.278 0.333 0.412 rg
52. 418. Td
(Numeric scales and clinical tools matter, but they flatten the day. Your diary gives them context: when pain rose, what changed,) Tj
T* (what helped, what failed, and what function was lost.) Tj
ET
