/F2 11 Tf
12.6499999999999986 TL
0.059 0.09 0.165 rg
44. 378. Td
(What Makes a Record Clinically Strong) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
10.3499999999999996 TL
0.278 0.333 0.412 rg
52. 362. Td
(A week or more of dated entries. Specific location and timing. Real function impact. Medication timing and outcome. Honest) Tj
T* (variation. A structure that can be scanned fast without losing the truth.) Tj
